channel.title: Looking to gather staff for project RS sever
channel.description:
Okay, I have a goal to launch a successful Runescape private server. I have launched a few in the past years on my own, however, I just never had the time for them. I'm currently finished with school and between classes and work I actually have a lot of free time on my hands, so I want to try this one last time. This time I want to do it right though.
I want to put together a devoted team to help each play a vital role in creating a popular server. I want a committed team. So for the people who interested, here's what I'm looking for: I need a few coders, graphic designers (Website, Video making, and art), moderators, and administrators. Looking for people with some experience and commitment. I don't know what type of server to make nor a version, so that's something I would like to discuss after I gather people. Any questions, feel free to ask.
If this topic goes into any conflict with forum rules please tell me the appropriate section to post this.
